<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="HISTORY"><a class="permalink" href="#HISTORY">HISTORY</a></h1>
The <code class="Nm">mlxctl</code> command first appeared in
  <span class="Ux">NetBSD 1.5.3</span>, and was based on the
  <code class="Ic">mlxcontrol</code> utility found in
  <span class="Ux">FreeBSD</span>.
</section>
<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="BUGS"><a class="permalink" href="#BUGS">BUGS</a></h1>
Modifying drive configuration is not yet supported.
<p class="Pp">Some commands do not work with older firmware revisions.</p>
<p class="Pp">Error log extraction is not yet supported.</p>
